Package: DPDE4PM
Title: A Method for Peak Merging Across Biological Replicates
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Helen", "Zhu", email = "helen.zhu@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A method for merging peaks called across biological replicates, in bed file format, identified across the transcriptome using variational Bayes on a Dirichlet prior to estimate a GMM model.
